{
  "text": "I have a question here, I believe, about the council. And Jim, who are the members and how does the council function? I am raw. The members of the council are regenatives from the Confederation and from those vibratory levels of your inner planes, bearing responsibility for your third density. The names are not important because there are no names your mind of body, spirit complexes, request names, and so in many cases the vibratory sound complexes which are consonant with the vibratory distortions of each entity are used. However, the name concept is not part of the council. If names are requested, we will attempt them how ever not all have chosen names. In number the council that sits in constant session, though varying in its members by means of a balancing which takes place what you would call irregularly his nine. The disportioned blending harmoniously, so that the ball of one prevails with ease when a need for thought is present. The council retains the distortion complex of this need, balancing it as described and then recommends what it considers as a propriet action. This includes one the duty of admitting the social memory complexes to the confederation to offering aid to those who are unsure how to aid the social memory complex requesting aid in a way consonant with both the call, the law, and the number of those calling. That is to say sometimes the resistance of the call. These are the prominent duties of the council. Who then offer consensus and judgment thinking to the council. The council then may reconsider any questions.",
  "timestamps": {
    "segment": [
      {
        "segment": "I have a question here, I believe, about the council.",
        "start_offset": 32,
        "end_offset": 96,
        "start": 2.56,
        "end": 7.68
      },
      {
        "segment": "And Jim, who are the members and how does the council function?",
        "start_offset": 113,
        "end_offset": 218,
        "start": 9.040000000000001,
        "end": 17.44
      },
      {
        "segment": "I am raw.",
        "start_offset": 302,
        "end_offset": 358,
        "start": 24.16,
        "end": 28.64
      },
      {
        "segment": "The members of the council are regenatives from the Confederation and from those vibratory levels of your inner planes, bearing responsibility for your third density.",
        "start_offset": 387,
        "end_offset": 984,
        "start": 30.96,
        "end": 78.72
      },
      {
        "segment": "The names are not important because there are no names your mind of body, spirit complexes, request names, and so in many cases the vibratory sound complexes which are consonant with the vibratory distortions of each entity are used.",
        "start_offset": 1013,
        "end_offset": 1884,
        "start": 81.04,
        "end": 150.72
      },
      {
        "segment": "However, the name concept is not part of the council.",
        "start_offset": 1901,
        "end_offset": 2088,
        "start": 152.08,
        "end": 167.04
      },
      {
        "segment": "If names are requested, we will attempt them how ever not all have chosen names.",
        "start_offset": 2111,
        "end_offset": 2408,
        "start": 168.88,
        "end": 192.64000000000001
      },
      {
        "segment": "In number the council that sits in constant session, though varying in its members by means of a balancing which takes place what you would call irregularly his nine.",
        "start_offset": 2426,
        "end_offset": 2973,
        "start": 194.08,
        "end": 237.84
      },
      {
        "segment": "The disportioned blending harmoniously, so that the ball of one prevails with ease when a need for thought is present.",
        "start_offset": 4146,
        "end_offset": 4600,
        "start": 331.68,
        "end": 368.0
      },
      {
        "segment": "The council retains the distortion complex of this need, balancing it as described and then recommends what it considers as a propriet action.",
        "start_offset": 4623,
        "end_offset": 5112,
        "start": 369.84000000000003,
        "end": 408.96000000000004
      },
      {
        "segment": "This includes one the duty of admitting the social memory complexes to the confederation to offering aid to those who are unsure how to aid the social memory complex requesting aid in a way consonant with both the call, the law, and the number of those calling.",
        "start_offset": 5131,
        "end_offset": 6032,
        "start": 410.48,
        "end": 482.56
      },
      {
        "segment": "That is to say sometimes the resistance of the call.",
        "start_offset": 6041,
        "end_offset": 6173,
        "start": 483.28000000000003,
        "end": 493.84000000000003
      },
      {
        "segment": "These are the prominent duties of the council.",
        "start_offset": 6417,
        "end_offset": 6549,
        "start": 513.36,
        "end": 523.92
      },
      {
        "segment": "Who then offer consensus and judgment thinking to the council.",
        "start_offset": 6793,
        "end_offset": 6981,
        "start": 543.44,
        "end": 558.48
      },
      {
        "segment": "The council then may reconsider any questions.",
        "start_offset": 7003,
        "end_offset": 7132,
        "start": 560.24,
        "end": 570.5600000000001
      }
    ],
